<p>We listen to your requirements, understand the project scope, and provide guidance to get the best result</p>

<h4>2. Proposal</h4>
<p>We develop a comprehensive proposal for your internal review with timelines and cost</p>

<h4>3. Project Kick Off</h4>
<p>We begin work on the project and schedule regular status updates and feedback sessions</p>

<h4>4. Rapid Prototype</h4>
<p>In some cases we will initially develop a quick prototype to ensure full alignment with your vision</p>

<h4>5. Completion</h4>
<p>We deliver the completed project on time and on budget</p>

<h4>6. Documentation, Testing Tools, Training, and Integration Support</h4>
<p>Decentral Solutions provides full support to your in-house engineers to ensure smooth adoption of the product, and the tools to allow future in-house maintenance</p>

